---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---
<Layout title="Privacy Policy" description="How Studio Moire handles the information you share when you book, enquire, or create an account.">
  <section class="max-w-6xl mx-auto px-6 py-16">
    <div class="container-reading flex flex-col gap-4 text-ink leading-relaxed">
      <h1 class="font-display text-4xl mb-2">Privacy Policy</h1>
      <p class="text-mute">Last updated 2025. This is a plain-language summary for Studio Moire, Casablanca.</p>
      <h2 class="font-display text-2xl mt-4">What we collect</h2>
      <p>When you send a note, request a shoot, or create an account, we collect the details you give us — your name, email, phone, preferred dates, what you're looking for, and any access or accessibility notes.</p>
      <h2 class="font-display text-2xl mt-4">How we use it</h2>
      <p>We use your details only to reply to your request, arrange a shoot, and remember your saved preferences if you create an account. Booking and enquiry submissions create a contact record in our studio CRM.</p>
      <h2 class="font-display text-2xl mt-4">Your choices</h2>
      <p>You can ask us to update or delete your information at any time by writing to <a class="underline decoration-accent underline-offset-4" href="mailto:hello@studio-moire.example">hello@studio-moire.example</a>. Account holders can edit saved preferences from the account page.</p>
      <h2 class="font-display text-2xl mt-4">Contact</h2>
      <p>Studio Moire · 56 Lantern Court, Casablanca 1044, Morocco · +212 54 2344 6744.</p>
    </div>
  </section>
</Layout>
